# LED Fading Without analogWrite ðŸŒ—âœ¨

This project demonstrates how to fade an LED in and out using **manual PWM** with an Arduino â€” without using the built-in `analogWrite()` function.

---

## ðŸ”§ Project Overview

- Smoothly fades an LED from OFF to ON and back
- Uses software-based PWM using `digitalWrite()` and `delayMicroseconds()`
- Great for learning about timing and brightness control without hardware PWM

